{"tid":1389074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個岩岩畢業嘅中學生，我有野想講","createTime":"2019-07-30T21:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:37:15.000Z","uid":283239,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce4402bc9c45e5a81581be5d15e6da9a4df09c3","tid":1389074,"uid":283239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:26:02.000Z","msg":"p牌仔，上兩個禮拜先入藉I大<br />\n<br />\n呢幾次發夢，都有出嚟，做過前線，做過set陣<br />\n見到呢幾日有好心人出錢買野食比我地班細路<br />\n<br />\n我地好多謝你<br />\n<br />\n見過好多差唔多年紀嘅朋友仔，係瞞住屋企人出黎，用哂零用黎買裝備，甚至係比政見立場唔同嘅屋企人經濟封鎖，而空槍上陣<br />\n<br />\n有過前線經驗，我覺得唔需要買到飯糰或m記包入去，因為唔會有咁閒情逸致去食<br />\n普普通通一支水，一條能量棒就夠<br />\n<br />\n反而係散場，全日冇野落肚，消耗量又大<br />\n手頭緊嘅朋友仔真係淨係夠錢搭車返屋企<br />\n希望大家可以請下佢地，真係唔需要多，簡簡單單一個碟頭頹飯即可，太豪太豐富反而會唔敢放開食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">本人有番開pt所以剛好自給自足，所以有好心人遞m記包同乾糧，我都推卻，希望個包會幫到真係有需要嘅人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家見到D小朋友望住個銀包發愁，不妨問下有冇野要幫手</span>"},{"pid":"d194a8ad921f9079dd069315f24e48e0e52bc7f4","tid":1389074,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:12:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nbtw 入籍個籍竹花頭，唔係草花頭個藉"},{"pid":"ade0fe67b90684bffeea3914f12cdaf8d9213af9","tid":1389074,"uid":76902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPDHWDV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPDHWDV.png&h=a0c9cadb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/poUggDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpoUggDW.png&h=d95e1992&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2krDSg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2krDSg.png&h=bd29c3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXqnWDX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXqnWDX.png&h=475b8f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8qSzqD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu